{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3403460/extras/StoreTextHeaders_Control.png?t=1738363371\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3403460/extras/Fight2.gif?t=1738363371\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">An <strong>Evil AI</strong> called <strong>HIVE</strong> has gained sentience and conquered Planet-X! Now it's up to you to <strong>FIGHT BACK</strong> using a large range of vehicles. From a small and quick <strong>Weaponized Delivery Truck</strong> all the way to building sized <strong>Heavy Mechs</strong>.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Unlock new Vehicles and Weapons</strong> by completing missions and fighting against the ever-increasing threat of hostile machines. <strong>Equip Your Vehicle</strong> with newer and<strong> Stronger Weapons</strong>. And make use of <strong>Artillery Strikes</strong>, for when your weapons alone just aren't enough to stop a <strong>Horde of Killer Robots</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3403460/extras/StoreTextHeaders_Unlock.png?t=1738363371\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3403460/extras/Unlock2.gif?t=1738363371\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Invest in <strong>Unlocking High-Tech Equipment</strong> such as Lasers, Rail-Guns and Experimental Mechs. Or go all-in on Missile Barrages and Heavy Tanks.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The demo</strong> allows you to experiment with <strong>29 different weapons</strong>. With more to come in the full release!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3403460/extras/StoreTextHeaders_Fight.png?t=1738363371\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3403460/extras/AltFight2.gif?t=1738363371\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fight against a <strong>Large Variety</strong> of <strong>Attacking Automatons</strong>. Each with their own unique strengths and weaknesses for you to exploit. Deal with <strong>Swarms</strong> of <strong>Detonating Drones</strong> using grenades. Or bring in the big guns to take down <strong>Menacing Machines</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3403460/extras/StoreTextHeaders_SupportAbilities.png?t=1738363371\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3403460/extras/SupportAbility.gif?t=1738363371\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Deploy defensive <strong>Turrets</strong> to distract and damage your opponents! Or call in destructive <strong>Artillery Strikes</strong>! Using these abilities at the right time will be decisive in your fight against the <strong>Heinous Hordes</strong> of <strong>Killing Machines!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Control different vehicles. Including Mechs, Tanks and Cars </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Use a large variety of weapons </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Make use of powerful support abilities. Such as artillery strikes and deployable turrets </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Defeat the hordes of hostile robots</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Fight across the planet, with environments ranging from sandy dunes to frozen wastelands and from forests to cities</p></li></ul>",